text: Ali Magomedovich Aliyev (; born June 2, 1983) is a Russian amateur boxer who won a gold medal at the 2006 European Championships in 2006Results and silver at the 2006 World Cup. == References == == External links == * Category:Living people Category:1983 births Category:Sportspeople from Makhachkala Category:Russian male boxers Category:Bantamweight boxers
